###  Test Suite list ###
#
## This is the minimum set of tests to run
## to quickly validate SAL updates.
## It runs the setup verification tests,
## Script and Test CSC salgenerator tests,
## and the SAL unit tests, which require 
## the Script and Test CSCs to run.
#
#  Change the title of the test results
--name SimpleSalSetup
--output SimpleSalSetup

